panel.settings.home.feedback.app.descrip: The _Illinois_ app is the official campus app of the University of _Illinois_ Urbana-Champaign. The app is built on the Rokwire open source software platform. The Rokwire project and the _Illinois_ app are efforts of the Smart, Healthy Communities Initiative in the office of the Provost at the University of _Illinois_.
